<html>
	<head>
		<title>Test Page</title>
		<script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/c9acfba105.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/styles.css">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/nav-bar.css">
		<script src="js/jquery.js"></script>
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com">
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	</head>
	<body>
		<div id='root-div'>
			<div id='content-div'>
				<div id='title-bar'>
                    <div id='hamburger-bar'>
                        <i class="fas fa-bars" id='hamburger-button'></i>
                    </div>
                </div>

				<div id='nav-bar' style='display:none;'>
                    <i class="fas fa-times" id='nav-close'></i>
                    <ul id='nav-bar-list'>
                        <li><a href='/home'>Home</a></li>
                        <li><a href='/add'>Add Activity</a></li>
                        <li><a href='/report'>Report</a></li>
                        <li><a href='/details'>All Activities</a></li>
                        <li><a href='/help'>Help</a></li>
                        <li><a href='/'>Log Out</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
				
				<div class="home-content">
					<h1 id="mob-title">Help</h1>
					<div id="help-content">
						<p>Since our app is new, we would like to have some guidances in order to have a better idea of how to use the app.</p>
						<p class='question' id='q1'>1. When does a report begin?<i class="fas fa-angle-down drop-down-button" id='bq1'></i></p>
						<p class='answer answer-invisible' id='aq1'>For every week, a report begins on Sunday.</p>
						<p class='question' id='q2'>2. Can an activity exceed 24 hours a day?<i class="fas fa-angle-down drop-down-button" id='bq2'></i></p>
						<p class='answer answer-invisible' id='aq2'>An activity cannot exceed 24 hours per day.</p>
						<p class='question' id='q3'>3. Where can I find all the options?<i class="fas fa-angle-down drop-down-button" id='bq3'></i></p>
						<p class='answer answer-invisible' id='aq3'>You can flexibly go to different pages by click/tapping the menu button on the top right, and see the options of where to go.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div id='buttons'>
					<a href='/home'>
						<div id='add-button'>Home</div>
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>

	<script src='js/navbar.js'></script>
	<script src='js/cookies.js'></script>
	<script>
		var username = getCookie('username', document.cookie);
		if(username === '') {
			// Not logged in
			window.location.href = '/';
		}
	</script>

	<script>
		$(document).ready(() => {
			$('p[id^=q]').click((e) => {
				var answerId = '#a' + e.currentTarget.id;
				var buttonId = '#b' + e.currentTarget.id;
				$(answerId).toggleClass('answer-invisible');
				if($(answerId).hasClass('answer-invisible')) {
					$(buttonId).removeClass('fa-angle-up');
					$(buttonId).addClass('fa-angle-down');
				} else {
					$(buttonId).removeClass('fa-angle-down');
					$(buttonId).addClass('fa-angle-up');
				}
			});
		});
	</script>
</html>
